|accessdate=2008-10-06}}</ref> Ethen dowr ha perthyglow polter yw res dh’aga furvya. Y krysir bos an polter a dheu a gorrveyn kowas po loskvenedhyow. <ref>[https://www.metoffice.gov.uk/weather/learn-about/weather/types-of-weather/clouds/other-clouds/noctilucent]</ref> Yma hwithrans a-dhiwedhes ow leverel  i dhe vos moy kemmyn  awos tommheans ollvysel ha moy a ethen dowr y’n ayrgylgh. <ref>[https://phys.org/news/2018-07-climate-night-shining-clouds-visible.html]</ref>

